==English==
===Noun===
'''life-buoy'''
#a [[torus]]-shaped object of [[density]] low enough to keep a person, which usually slips his head, shoulders, and arms through it, [[afloat]]. Often coloured white and bright red to be seen from great distance and in [[adverse]] wheather or light conditions. [[Design]]ed to be thrown after a person that went [[overboard]]; hence often found attached to [[railing]]s close to water, e.g. on a ship.
